The,W,C,Geolocation,API,defines,a,specification,for,an,API,that,provides,access,to,geolocation,information,for,the,hosting,device,in,the,form,of,latitude,and,longitude,coordinates,It,allows,both,one,shot,and,repeated,position,updates,as,well,as,the,querying,of,cached,positions,This,document,is,a,stable,recommendation,that,may,be,cited,or,used,as,reference,material